na at MetLife** — a rematch of the \"Finalissima\" dynamic. Spain's generational core at peak age (Yamal, Pedri, Cubarsí) versus a transitioning Argentina; Spain's press and control win out. France takes third over England.\n\n**Golden Boot:** Kylian Mbappé — a semifinal run plus penalties duty for France. **Dark horse:** Norway — group runners-up over Senegal and a genuine scare for Brazil, with Haaland among the top scorers.",
